{"title":"给你的Hexo静态博客部署LateX支持","uid":"dcdcee834f273ccf9b6767caa4fb38f8","slug":"LateX-Settings","date":"2025-07-11T09:54:59.000Z","updated":"2025-07-11T10:05:06.268Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/LateX-Settings.json","cover":null,"content":"<h1 id=\"给你的Hexo静态博客部署-latex-支持\"><a href=\"#给你的Hexo静态博客部署-latex-支持\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"给你的Hexo静态博客部署 $latex$ 支持\"></a>给你的Hexo静态博客部署 $latex$ 支持</h1><p>众所周知，hexo搭建的静态博客非常nice，但是对于OIer来说没有LateX公式支持，岂不是美中不足？</p>\n<script type=\"math/tex; mode=display\">Designed By FrankWkd</script><h2 id=\"方案一（推荐）：hexo-filter-mathjax-hexo-renderer-pandoc\"><a href=\"#方案一（推荐）：hexo-filter-mathjax-hexo-renderer-pandoc\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"方案一（推荐）：hexo-filter-mathjax + hexo-renderer-pandoc\"></a>方案一（推荐）：hexo-filter-mathjax + hexo-renderer-pandoc</h2><ul>\n<li><p>hexo-filter-mathjax官方教程：<a href=\"https://github.com/next-theme/hexo-filter-mathjax\">https://github.com/next-theme/hexo-filter-mathjax</a></p>\n</li>\n<li><p>hexo-renderer-pandoc官方教程：<a href=\"https://github.com/wzpan/hexo-renderer-pandoc\">https://github.com/wzpan/hexo-renderer-pandoc</a></p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p>先把所有其他hexo math有关的npm包卸掉，比方说这些：</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">npm un hexo-math --save</span><br><span class=\"line\">npm un hexo-renderer-markdown --save</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>然后安装hexo-filter-mathjax：</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">npm i hexo-filter-mathjax --save</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>然后安装pandoc: <a href=\"https://pandoc.org/installing.html\">https://pandoc.org/installing.html</a></p>\n<div class=\"custom-quote tip\">\n<span class=\"custom-quote-svg\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" data-reactroot=\"\">\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M20.86 14.13C20 14.7 19.56 15.74 19.77 16.76C20.13 18.55 18.55 20.13 16.76 19.77C15.74 19.57 14.7 20 14.13 20.86C13.12 22.38 10.89 22.38 9.88 20.86C9.3 20 8.26 19.56 7.24 19.77C5.45 20.13 3.87 18.55 4.23 16.76C4.43 15.74 4 14.7 3.14 14.13C1.62 13.12 1.62 10.89 3.14 9.88C4 9.3 4.44 8.26 4.23 7.24C3.87 5.45 5.45 3.87 7.24 4.23C8.26 4.44 9.3 4 9.87 3.14C10.88 1.62 13.11 1.62 14.12 3.14C14.7 4 15.74 4.44 16.76 4.23C18.55 3.87 20.13 5.45 19.77 7.24C19.56 8.26 20 9.3 20.86 9.87C22.38 10.88 22.38 13.12 20.86 14.13Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M12.01 15C12.01 14.5 12.01 14.5 12.01 14.5C12.04 13.75 13 13.46 14.04 12.2C14.41 11.74 14.69 11.41 14.86 10.85C15.15 9.95 14.92 9.18 14.86 9.02C14.8 8.79 14.52 8 13.72 7.46C13.06 7.02 12.42 7 12.14 7C11.9 7 11.36 7 10.78 7.3C10.28 7.56 9.98 7.9 9.83 8.1C9.24 8.82 9.06 9.63 9 10.06\"></path>\n<path stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M11.99 18H12.01\"></path>\n</svg></span>\n<p class=\"custom-quote-title\">提示</p>\n<p>Debian系好像可以直接用apt安装：<br><figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">sudo apt install pandoc</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p>\n\n</div>\n<p>然后安装hexo-renderer-pandoc：</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">npm i hexo-renderer-pandoc --save</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>然后在想开启MathJax的博客前面加上<code>mathjax: true</code>，比如</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">---</span><br><span class=\"line\">title: On the Electrodynamics of Moving Bodies</span><br><span class=\"line\">categories: Physics</span><br><span class=\"line\">date: 1905-06-30 12:00:00</span><br><span class=\"line\">mathjax: true</span><br><span class=\"line\">---</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>如果懒得在每篇博客前面加上<code>mathjax: true</code>，就在<code>_config.yml</code>里加上</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">mathjax:</span><br><span class=\"line\">  every_page: true</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>这样所有博客都会自动使用MathJax。然后就可以像在Latex里面一样编辑公式了：</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">$\\underset&#123;theta&#125;&#123;\\bowtie&#125;$</span><br><span class=\"line\">$N^+ = \\&#123;x | x\\in N \\wedge x \\ne 0\\&#125;$</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>但是默认的markdown语法跟github的markdown语法不一样。</p>\n<p>这篇文章提供了一个workaround：<a href=\"https://blog.rule55.com/hexo/\">https://blog.rule55.com/hexo/</a>，即在<code>_config.yml</code>里加入</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br><span class=\"line\">10</span><br><span class=\"line\">11</span><br><span class=\"line\">12</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"># Configure pandoc to use all github markdown format extensions</span><br><span class=\"line\"># extensions as of 2018 is an undocumented feature of hexo-renderer-pandoc</span><br><span class=\"line\"># Adding all extensions for github so we don&#x27;t have to change index.js of</span><br><span class=\"line\"># hexo-renderer-pandoc.</span><br><span class=\"line\">pandoc:</span><br><span class=\"line\">  extensions:</span><br><span class=\"line\">    - -implicit_figures # 防止在图片后面将方括号里的东西作为caption。</span><br><span class=\"line\">    - +gfm_auto_identifiers+angle_brackets_escapable # Not available in pandoc 1.16</span><br><span class=\"line\">    - +pipe_tables+raw_html+fenced_code_blocks</span><br><span class=\"line\">    - -ascii_identifiers+backtick_code_blocks+autolink_bare_uris</span><br><span class=\"line\">    - +intraword_underscores+strikeout+hard_line_breaks+emoji</span><br><span class=\"line\">    - +shortcut_reference_links</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>其中<code>-implicit_figures</code>的来源：<a href=\"https://github.com/wzpan/hexo-renderer-pandoc/issues/34\">https://github.com/wzpan/hexo-renderer-pandoc/issues/34</a></p>\n<p>但是感觉这样还是不太优雅。要是可以直接像其他渲染器那样直接传进一个<code>gfm</code>就好了。好像pandoc是有这个参数的，但是我在插件里的<code>index.js</code>里把<code>markdown-smart</code>改成<code>gfm</code>，并且改了后面的<code>register</code>之后没反应，不知道为什么。</p>\n<h2 id=\"方案二：hexo-renderer-markdown\"><a href=\"#方案二：hexo-renderer-markdown\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"方案二：hexo-renderer-markdown\"></a>方案二：hexo-renderer-markdown</h2><p>参考：<br><a href=\"https://github.com/wujun234/hexo-theme-tree/issues/14\">https://github.com/wujun234/hexo-theme-tree/issues/14</a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://github.com/niemingzhao/hexo-renderer-markdown\">https://github.com/niemingzhao/hexo-renderer-markdown</a></p>\n<figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">npm un hexo-renderer-marked --save</span><br><span class=\"line\">npm i hexo-renderer-markdown --save</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>但是hexo-renderer-markdown好像有high severity vulnerabilities。而且仍然有些Latex公式不能正常显示。比如<code>\\underset&#123;theta&#125;&#123;\\bowtie&#125;</code>。而且单行公式里如果有<code>\\&#125;</code>的话公式就不能正常显示了。</p>\n<h2 id=\"方案三：hexo-math-hexo-renderer-marked\"><a href=\"#方案三：hexo-math-hexo-renderer-marked\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"方案三：hexo-math + hexo-renderer-marked\"></a>方案三：hexo-math + hexo-renderer-marked</h2><p>hexo-math官方教程: <a href=\"https://github.com/hexojs/hexo-math\">https://github.com/hexojs/hexo-math</a></p>\n<figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">npm i hexo-renderer-marked --save</span><br><span class=\"line\">npm i hexo-math --save</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>但是由于hexo-renderer-marked的原因，hexo-math的公式编辑只能是这种形式：</p>\n<ul>\n<li>katex公式</li>\n</ul>\n<figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">&#123;% katex %&#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">c = \\pm\\sqrt&#123;a^2 + b^2&#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">&#123;% endkatex %&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<ul>\n<li>mathjax公式</li>\n</ul>\n<figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">&#123;% mathjax %&#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">\\frac&#123;1&#125;&#123;x^2-1&#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">&#123;% endmathjax %&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<h2 id=\"失败的方案：hexo-math-hexo-renderer-kramed\"><a href=\"#失败的方案：hexo-math-hexo-renderer-kramed\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"失败的方案：hexo-math + hexo-renderer-kramed\"></a>失败的方案：hexo-math + hexo-renderer-kramed</h2><p>教程：<a href=\"https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/108766968\">https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/108766968</a>。</p>\n<p>公式会消失。这可能是因为hexo-renderer-kramed只支持到hexo 3，然后我用的是hexo 5。</p>\n<p>hexo-renderer-kramed: <a href=\"https://github.com/sun11/hexo-renderer-kramed\">https://github.com/sun11/hexo-renderer-kramed</a></p>\n","feature":true,"text":"给你的Hexo静态博客部署 $latex$ 支持众所周知，hexo搭建的静态博客非常nice，但是对于OIer来说没有LateX公式支持，岂不是美中不足？ De...","permalink":"/post/LateX-Settings","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":"2.9k","symbolsTime":"3 mins."},"categories":[{"name":"编辑，建站","slug":"编辑，建站","count":1,"path":"api/categories/编辑，建站.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"LateX","slug":"LateX","count":1,"path":"api/tags/LateX.json"}],"toc":"<ol class=\"toc\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-1\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E7%BB%99%E4%BD%A0%E7%9A%84Hexo%E9%9D%99%E6%80%81%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2%E9%83%A8%E7%BD%B2-latex-%E6%94%AF%E6%8C%81\"><span class=\"toc-text\">给你的Hexo静态博客部署 $latex$ 支持</span></a><ol class=\"toc-child\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E6%96%B9%E6%A1%88%E4%B8%80%EF%BC%88%E6%8E%A8%E8%8D%90%EF%BC%89%EF%BC%9Ahexo-filter-mathjax-hexo-renderer-pandoc\"><span class=\"toc-text\">方案一（推荐）：hexo-filter-mathjax + hexo-renderer-pandoc</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E6%96%B9%E6%A1%88%E4%BA%8C%EF%BC%9Ahexo-renderer-markdown\"><span class=\"toc-text\">方案二：hexo-renderer-markdown</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E6%96%B9%E6%A1%88%E4%B8%89%EF%BC%9Ahexo-math-hexo-renderer-marked\"><span class=\"toc-text\">方案三：hexo-math + hexo-renderer-marked</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E5%A4%B1%E8%B4%A5%E7%9A%84%E6%96%B9%E6%A1%88%EF%BC%9Ahexo-math-hexo-renderer-kramed\"><span class=\"toc-text\">失败的方案：hexo-math + hexo-renderer-kramed</span></a></li></ol></li></ol>","author":{"name":"FrankWkd","slug":"blog-author","avatar":"https://cdn.luogu.com.cn/upload/image_hosting/ofl7t46i.png","link":"/","description":"苦心人、天不负，卧薪尝胆，三千越甲可吞吴。 <br /> @ <b>博客园：FrankWkd</b>","socials":{"github":"https://github.com/FrankWkd-Pro","twitter":"","stackoverflow":"","wechat":"","qq":"","weibo":"","zhihu":"https://www.zhihu.com/people/frankwkd","csdn":"https://blog.csdn.net/frankwkd","juejin":"","customs":{}}},"mapped":true,"hidden":false,"prev_post":{},"next_post":{"title":"Hello World!","uid":"2660108b1f08a72a4a842a5343a0caf5","slug":"Hello-World","date":"2025-07-11T00:35:42.000Z","updated":"2025-07-11T00:49:10.770Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/Hello-World.json","cover":null,"text":"This is the first day that i heve my own blog.Thanks: Powered By Hexo and Github...","permalink":"/post/Hello-World","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":"2.4k","symbolsTime":"2 mins."},"categories":[],"tags":[{"name":"Others","slug":"Others","count":1,"path":"api/tags/Others.json"}],"author":{"name":"FrankWkd","slug":"blog-author","avatar":"https://cdn.luogu.com.cn/upload/image_hosting/ofl7t46i.png","link":"/","description":"苦心人、天不负，卧薪尝胆，三千越甲可吞吴。 <br /> @ <b>博客园：FrankWkd</b>","socials":{"github":"https://github.com/FrankWkd-Pro","twitter":"","stackoverflow":"","wechat":"","qq":"","weibo":"","zhihu":"https://www.zhihu.com/people/frankwkd","csdn":"https://blog.csdn.net/frankwkd","juejin":"","customs":{}}},"feature":true}}